casebody.data:
No. 406,

Misc.

Miller v. Rhay, Penitentiary Superintendent. Petitioner pro se. John J. O’Connell, Attorney General of Washington, and Stephen C. Way, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Sup Ct. Wash. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certio-rari granted. Case transferred to appellate docket.
